                                <font face="times new roman,times" size="3">Parent class linking to  information about the patient while in the care of other providers.</font>
                            </strong>
                        </p>
                    </text>
                </otherAnnotation>
            </annotations>
            <attribute conformance="R" fixedValue="PAT"
